# Tell GitHub Linguist to ignore all files in /archive/
archive/** linguist-vendored

# Tell GitHub Linguist to track Markdown files
*.md linguist-detectable=true

# Tell GitHub Linguist to ignore all meta.md files
*-meta.md linguist-vendored

# Tell GitHub Linguist to ignore the readme, ideas, and names files
license.md linguist-vendored
readme.md linguist-vendored
stories/ideas.md linguist-vendored
stories/names.md linguist-vendored

# Auto detect text files and perform LF normalization
* text=auto
